    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>One angry fishy. One cruel world. One nuclear missile.</strong></u></h2><br><strong><u>Welcome to the Zakaria Trench!</u></strong><br>Beneath a small bay between two islands lies a deep trench with sunken cities, military bases, submerged nuclear silos, deep wilds, and many other fun tourist spots for the family. There are 9 areas total, so I hope you have a map, because you are going to need it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/803948b88966ce91ec088b85d4817b1a.poster.avif?t=1767557825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/803948b88966ce91ec088b85d4817b1a.webm?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/803948b88966ce91ec088b85d4817b1a.mp4?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Make Them All Pay</u></strong><br>Armed with only your teeth, a hunger for vengeance, and whatever you find along the way, you must swim to the bottom of the trench to reach the sunken nuclear missile. You are not alone, however, so you might as well stir up as much mayhem as possible along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/83719f22c8a78c5be05680bd998f3c2e.poster.avif?t=1767557825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/83719f22c8a78c5be05680bd998f3c2e.webm?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/83719f22c8a78c5be05680bd998f3c2e.mp4?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>You Will Stop at Nothing</strong></u><br>No matter how big or fierce you foes are, they will bleed out for the crimes commited against you. You will be heard. And they will be dead.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/e15c487ccf3eac1fc4755cc6633b00b1.poster.avif?t=1767557825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/e15c487ccf3eac1fc4755cc6633b00b1.webm?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/e15c487ccf3eac1fc4755cc6633b00b1.mp4?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>There's Always More</strong></u><br>Find arcade minigames, pets, abilities, secrets, characters, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/732a0ee3a2122eb5977f59801a3d22dd.poster.avif?t=1767557825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/732a0ee3a2122eb5977f59801a3d22dd.webm?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371040/extras/732a0ee3a2122eb5977f59801a3d22dd.mp4?t=1767557825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
